title: Moving copy of Caffe2 protos back to build_pytorch_libs.sh
body_html: This way it shows up in all current and future setup.py commands, as otherwise we'd have to override every once to have them all call copy_protos. This is needed because the nightly packages still do not include caffe2_pb2, because setup.py bdist does not go through setup.py install or setup.py develop
